  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together miso paste, orange juice, and olive oil.",
    "Add the natto to the bowl and stir until well combined.",
    "Stir in chopped parsley, cilantro, salt, and black pepper.",
    "In a separate large bowl, prepare the couscous according to package instructions.",
    "Fluff the cooked couscous with a fork and stir in lemon zest.",
    "Add the natto mixture to the couscous and stir until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and bake for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes before serving."
  ],
